Title: Tools for supersymmetry
Authors: Antoine Van Proeyen
Comments: 49 pages; Lectures in the spring school in Calimanesti, Romania,
  April 1998; v2: one typo corrected, and some clarification in the text; v3: a
  sign in (2.62) corrected; v4: a factor in (3.44); v5: correction to real
  forms of exceptional superalgebras; v6: sign correction in (3.25)
Report-no: KUL-TF-99/37
\\
  This is an elementary introduction to basic tools of supersymmetry: the
spacetime symmetries, gauge theory and its application in gravity, spinors and
superalgebras. Special attention is devoted to conformal and anti-de Sitter
algebras.
